sentence: How many sections are there for EECS 280 ?
sentence-with-vars: How many sections are there for department0 number0 ?
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SECTION_NUMBER ) FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 280 ;
